name: Google Alternative (very simple CSS)
description:
This is a user style CSS for "Startpage.com".
It makes Startpage a visual Google-Alt-Clone.
There is also an alternative Logo included.

Easy to maintain - only a few lines of CSS.
Code is very simple, but efficient and effective.

Here you find a FAVICON in a matching visual style:
https://imgur.com/zaDTNnf

You can use a favicon-customizer (Firefox addon) to customize your favicon for each individual URL/domain.

.
